    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, with only minor, age-appropriate imperfections that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, the dashboard remains crack-free, and all power features\u2014including the climate control and premium sound system\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced regularly with high-quality fluids, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power without hesitation. The suspension is tight, providing a composed ride, and the brakes offer firm, confident feedback. With a clean title and a documented maintenance history, this car represents a turnkey opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable and aesthetically pleasing daily driver.",
