      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for all your road trips and daily commutes. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is totally ready to hit the road whenever you are. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
