    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera. Powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, this 996.2 generation features VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a firm, communicative clutch pedal. Performance is anchored by a rigid chassis with a multi-link rear geometry that minimizes toe-steer. Noteworthy technical updates include an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently flushed cooling system with a low-temp thermostat. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for exceptional thermal management. This is a driver-focused example in good condition, prioritizing mechanical integrity and kinematic excellence over concours aesthetics.",
